  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_165",
    "english": "A lesser demon that dwells in the Demon Realm. They can be made as servants at the cost of demonic energy and be raised as pets, or a secret weapon. They have a meek hypnotic ability, alluring the opponent as their master commands to make them allies, or confuse the enemy's senses to bring chaos.",
